<s> As I understand it, you are pointing out that it is possible to do things like client-side validation or processing of forms.  </s>
<s> In this case it is important to recognise that there are user agents which do not support client-side scripting, and will not be able to use the pages unless thre is some server-side equivalent of the functionality.  </s>
