<s> CMN THe problem with relying on tables is that there are accessibility solutions inwide use which do not satisfactorily linearise tables into something which preserves the meaning defined by the layout.  </s>
<s> Therefore, using tables to provide this meaning is an accessibility problem.  </s>
<s> The WCAG solution is to require that content is made in a form where the semantics do not rely on the layout of the content, but are expressed in the markup.  </s>
